<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>파드 서버 2기 대망의 첫 과제 시작!!</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: white;
            color: darkseagreen;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .jumbotron {
            background-color: transparent;
            animation: fadeIn 7s;
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .text-below-logo {
            z-index: 99;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        .blinking-text {
            margin-top: 20px;
            animation: blink 5s infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <img src="/img/파드서버로고.png" alt="파드 서버 로고" class="logo">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-below-logo">파드 서버 2기</h1>
        <h3 class="blinking-text text-below-logo">-내가 리눅스다 채우 캐릭캐릭채린지 이병윤성현! zㅣ존주현 브론즈 태형 탱글보이하민-</h3>
        <h3 class="blinking-text text-below-logo">파이팅!!!</h3>
        <p class="lead text-below-logo">대망의 첫 과제 시작!!</p>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>